Loop¶

%%time

df = []
alpha = 0.001
lags = 11
for expt, grp in file.items():
    hf = np.array(grp['hyperflow'])
    spks = np.array(grp['spks'], dtype=float)
    good = ~np.array(grp['badspks'])
    good = np.where(good)[0]
    hf, spks = setup_supervised_data(lags, good, hf, spks)
    hf_r, spks_r = setup_repeat_data(grp, lags, 'hyperflowR')
    x = flatten_stim(hf)

    print(f"fitting {expt} . . .")
    for i in range(spks.shape[-1]):
        useful = i in cfg.useful_cells.get(expt, {})
        kf = KFold(5, shuffle=True, random_state=42)
        for fold, (trn, vld) in enumerate(kf.split(x)):
            glm = PoissonRegressor(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x[trn], spks[:, i][trn])
            pred = glm.predict(x[vld])
            nnll = null_adj_ll(spks[vld][:, i], pred)
            print(expt, i, fold, nnll)
            df.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['nnll'],
                'score': [nnll],
            })
        if spks_r is not None:
            glm = PoissonRegressor(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x, spks[:, i])
            pred = glm.predict(flatten_stim(hf_r))
            true = np.nanmean(spks_r, 1)[i]
            r2 = r2_score(true, pred) * 100
            df.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['r2'],
                'score': [r2],
            })
            plt.plot(true, label=f"{expt}, ch{i}.")
            plt.plot(pred, label=f"r2 = {r2:0.1f}%")
            plt.legend()
            plt.show()

        print('_' * 70)
    print('_' * 70 + '\n' + '_' * 70)
    print('\n\n')

df = pd.DataFrame(merge_dicts(df))
print('Done.')
file.close()

dim = 256

rng = get_rng()
w = rng.normal(size=(8, dim))
plt.imshow(w, aspect=5);

file = h5py.File(cfg.h_file, 'r')

%%time

df_reservoir = []
alpha = 0.1
lags = 11
for expt, grp in file.items():
    hf = np.array(grp['hyperflow'])
    spks = np.array(grp['spks'], dtype=float)
    good = ~np.array(grp['badspks'])
    good = np.where(good)[0]
    hf, spks = setup_supervised_data(lags, good, hf, spks)
    hf_r, spks_r = setup_repeat_data(grp, lags, 'hyperflowR')
    
    x = np.einsum('ijk, kl -> ijl', hf, w)
    x = flatten_stim(np.tanh(x))
    
    if hf_r is not None:
        x_r = np.einsum('ijk, kl -> ijl', hf_r, w)
        x_r = flatten_stim(np.tanh(x_r))

    print(f"fitting {expt} . . .")
    for i in range(spks.shape[-1]):
        useful = i in cfg.useful_cells.get(expt, {})
        kf = KFold(5, shuffle=True, random_state=42)
        for fold, (trn, vld) in enumerate(kf.split(x)):
            glm = PoissonRegressor(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x[trn], spks[:, i][trn])
            pred = glm.predict(x[vld])
            nnll = null_adj_ll(spks[vld][:, i], pred)
            print(expt, i, fold, nnll)
            df_reservoir.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['nnll'],
                'score': [nnll],
            })
        if spks_r is not None:
            glm = PoissonRegressor(
                alpha=alpha,
                max_iter=int(1e4),
            ).fit(x, spks[:, i])
            pred = glm.predict(x_r)
            true = np.nanmean(spks_r, 1)[i]
            r2 = r2_score(true, pred) * 100
            df_reservoir.append({
                'expt': [expt],
                'channel': [i],
                'useful': [useful],
                'fold': [fold],
                'alpha': [alpha],
                'label': ['r2'],
                'score': [r2],
            })
            plt.plot(true, label=f"{expt}, ch{i}.")
            plt.plot(pred, label=f"r2 = {r2:0.1f}%")
            plt.legend()
            plt.show()

        print('_' * 70)
    print('_' * 70 + '\n' + '_' * 70)
    print('\n\n')

df_reservoir = pd.DataFrame(merge_dicts(df_reservoir))
print('Done.')
file.close()

Try 16¶

cfg = ConfigVAE()
file = h5py.File(cfg.h_file, 'r')

expt = 'clu267'
grp = file[expt]

lags = 11

spks = np.array(grp['spks'], dtype=float)
good = ~np.array(grp['badspks'])
good = np.where(good)[0]

hf = np.array(grp['hyperflow'])
hf = HyperFlow(
    opticflow=hf[:, 2:],
    center=hf[:, :2],
    size=32,
    sres=2,
    radius=8,
)
stim = hf.compute_hyperflow()
stim, spks = setup_supervised_data(lags, good, stim, spks)

if 'repeats' in grp:
    
    hf_r = np.array(grp['repeats']['hyperflowR'])
    hf_r = HyperFlow(
        opticflow=hf_r[:, 2:],
        center=hf_r[:, :2],
        size=32,
        sres=2,
        radius=8,
    )
    stim_r = hf_r.compute_hyperflow()
    _, spks_r, intvl = setup_repeat_data(grp, lags, 'hyperflowR')
    stim_r = time_embed(stim_r, lags, intvl)
file.close()

((36591, 11, 16, 16, 2), (201, 11, 16, 16, 2))

stim /= sd

        tol=1e-4,
    ).fit(flatten_stim(stim[trn]), spks[trn][:, ii])
    pred = glm.predict(flatten_stim(stim[vld]))
    nnll = null_adj_ll(spks[vld][:, ii], pred)
    nnll_all_folds.append(nnll)
    
    r2 = r2_score(spks[vld][:, ii], pred) * 100
    r, pval = sp_stats.pearsonr(spks[vld][:, ii], pred)
    print(f"f{fold}.\tnnll = {nnll:0.3f},\tr2 = {r2:0.1f}%, r = {r:0.3f}")
print(f"avg nnll: {np.mean(nnll_all_folds)}")

stim_log = np.zeros_like(stim)
for i, x in enumerate(stim):
    rho, theta = to_polar(x)
    log_rho = np.log(np.maximum(rho, 1e-10))
    theta[rho == 0] = 0
    vx = log_rho * np.cos(theta)
    vy = log_rho * np.sin(theta)
    vx[rho == 0] = 0
    vy[rho == 0] = 0
    stim_log[i, ..., 0] = vx
    stim_log[i, ..., 1] = vy
